quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  34,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  34,1,sab tareef khuda hi ko ( sazawar ) hai ( jo sab cheezon ka maalik hai yani ) woh ke jo kuch asmano mein hai aur jo kuch zameen mein hai sab isi ka hai aur akhirat mein bhi isi ki tareef hai. aur woh hikmat wala khabardaar hai
  34,2,jo kuch zameen mein daakhil hota hai aur jo is mein se nikalta hai aur jo aasman se uterta hai aur jo is par charhata hai sab is ko maloom hai. aur woh meharban ( aur ) bakhsnay wala hai
  34,3,aur kafir kehte hain ke ( qayamat ki ) gharri hum par nahi aeye gi. keh do kyun nahi ( aeye gi ) mere perwar-digaar ki qasam woh tum par zaroor aakar rahay gi ( woh perwar-digaar ) ghaib ka jan-nay wala ( hai ) zarra bhar cheez bhi is se posheeda nahi ( nah ) asmano mein aur nah zameen mein aur koi cheez zarray se choti ya barri aisi nahi magar kitaab roshan mein ( likhi hui ) hai
  34,4,is liye ke jo log imaan laaye aur amal naik karte rahay un ko badla day. yahi hain jin ke liye bakhshish aur izzat ki rozi hai
  34,5,aur jinhon ne hamari aayton mein koshish ki ke hamein hara den ge. un ke liye sakht dard dainay walay azaab ki saza hai
  34,6,aur jin logon ko ilm diya gaya hai woh jantay hain ke jo ( quran ) tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se tum par nazil howa hai woh haq hai. aur ( khuday-e ) ghalib aur sazawar tareef ka rasta batata hai
  34,7,aur kafir kehte hain ke bhala hum tumhe aisa aadmi bitayen jo tumhe khabar deta hai ke jab tum ( mar kar ) bilkul Parah Parah ho jao ge to naye suray se peda hogay
  34,8,ya to is ne khuda par jhoot bandh liya hai. ya usay junoon hai. baat yeh hai ke jo log akhirat par imaan nahi rakhtay woh aafat aur parlay darjay ki gumraahi mein ( mubtala ) hain
  34,9,kiya unhon ne is ko nahi dekha jo un ke agay aur peechay hai yani aasman aur zameen. agar hum chahain to un ko zameen mein dhansa den ya un par aasman ke tukre gira den. is mein har bande ke liye jo rujoo karne wala hai aik nishani hai
  34,10,aur hum ne dawod ko apni taraf se bartari bakhsh thi. ae paharro un ke sath tasbeeh karo aur parindon ko ( un ka maskhar kardiya ) aur un ke liye hum ne lohay ko naram kardiya+A3639
  34,11,ke kushadah zarrain banaao aur kudiyon ko andazay se joro aur naik amal karo. jo amal tum karte ho mein un ko dekhnay wala hon
  34,12,aur howa ko ( hum ne ) Sulaiman ka tabay kardiya tha is ki subah ki manzil aik mahinay ki raah hoti aur shaam ki manzil bhi mahinay bhar ki hoti. aur un ke liye hum ne tanbay ka chashma baha diya tha aur junoo mein se aisay they jo un ke perwar-digaar ke hukum se un ke agay kaam karte they. aur jo koi un mein se hamaray hukum se phiray ga is ko hum ( jahannum ki ) aag ka maza chkhayin ge
  34,13,woh jo chahtay yeh un ke liye banatay yani qilay aur mujasmay aur ( barray barray ) lagan jaisay talaab aur digin jo aik hi jagah rakhi rahen. ae dawod ki aulaad ( mera ) shukar karo aur mere bundon mein shukar guzar thoray hain
  34,14,phir jab hum ne un ke liye mout ka hukum sadirkiya to kisi cheez se un ka marna maloom nah howa magar ghinn ke keeray se jo un ke asa ko khata raha. jab asa gir para tab junoo ko maloom howa ( aur kehnay lagey ) ke agar woh ghaib jantay hotay to zillat ki takleef mein nah rehtay
  34,15,( ahal ) Saba ke liye un ke maqam bodobash mein aik nishani thi ( yani ) do baagh ( aik ) dahni taraf aur ( aik ) baen taraf. apne perwar-digaar ka rizaq khao aur is ka shukar karo. ( yahan tumahray rehne ko yeh ) pakeeza shehar hai aur ( wahan bakhsnay ko ) khuday-e Ghafar
  34,16,to unhon ne ( shukarguzari se ) munh phair liya pas hum ne un par zor ka selaab chore diya aur inhen un ke baghoon ke badlay do aisay baagh diye jin ke meway bad mazah they aur jin mein kuch to جھاؤ tha aur thori si beriyaan
  34,17,yeh hum ne un ki nashukri ki un ko saza di. aur hum saza nashukray hi ko diya karte hain
  34,18,aur hum ne un ke aur ( shaam ki ) un bustiyon ke darmain jin mein hum ne barket di thi ( aik dosray ke mut-tasil ) dehaat banaye they jo samnay nazar atay they aur un mein aamad waraft ka andaza muqarrar kardiya tha ke raat din be khauf o khatar chaltay raho
  34,19,to unhon ne dua ki ke ae perwar-digaar hamari musafaton mein baad ( aur tole peda ) kardey aur ( is se ) unhon ne apne haq mein zulmkiya to hum ne ( inhen nabood karkay ) un ke afsaanay bnadiye aur inhen bilkul munhtashir kardiya. is mein har sabir o shakir ke liye nishanain hain
  34,20,aur shetan ne un ke baray mein apna khayaal sach kar dekhaya ke mominoun ki aik jamaat ke siwa woh is ke peechay chal parre
  34,21,aur is ka un par kuch zor nah tha magar ( hamara ) maqsood yeh tha ke jo log akhirat mein shak rakhtay hain un se un logon ko jo is par imaan rakhtay they mutamaiyaz (mumtaz) kar dein. aur tumhara perwar-digaar har cheez par nigehbaan hai
  34,22,keh do ke jin ko tum khuda ke siwa ( mabood ) khayaal karte ho un ko bulaao. woh asmano aur zameen mein zarra bhar cheez ke bhi maalik nahi hain aur nah un mein un ki shirkat hai aur nah un mein se koi khuda ka madadgaar hai
  34,23,aur khuda ke haan ( kisi ke liye ) sifarish faida nah day gi magar is ke liye jis ke baray mein woh ijazat bakhshay. yahan taq ke jab un ke dilon se iztiraab daur kardiya jaye ga to kahin ge tumahray perwar-digaar nekiya farmaya hai. ( farishtay ) kahin ge ke haq ( farmaya hai ) aur woh aliiiii rutba aur graami qader hai
  34,24,pucho ke tum ko asmano aur zameen se kon rizaq deta hai? kaho ke khuda aur hum ya tum ( ya to ) seedhay raste par hain ya Sarih gumraahi mein
  34,25,keh do ke nah hamaray gunaaho ki tum se prssh hogi aur nah tumahray aamaal ki hum se prssh hogi
  34,26,keh do ke hamara perwar-digaar hum ko jama kere ga phir hamaray darmain insaaf ke sath faisla kardey ga. aur woh khoob faisla karne wala aur sahib ilm hai
  34,27,kaho ke mujhe woh log to dikhao jin ko tum ne shareek ( khuda ) bana kar is ke sath mila rakha hai. koi nahi balkay wohi ( akela ) khuda ghalib ( aur ) hikmat wala hai
  34,28,aur ( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) hum ne tum ko tamam logon ke liye khushkhabri sunanay wala aur darane wala bana kar bheja hai lekin aksar log nahi jantay
  34,29,aur kehte hain agar tum sach kehte ho to yeh ( qayamat ka ) wada kab wuqoo mein aeye ga
  34,30,keh do ke tum se aik din ka wada hai jis se nah aik gharri peechay rahoge aur nah agay brhho ge
  34,31,aur jo kafir hain woh kehte hain ke hum nah to is quran ko manen ge aur nah un ( kitabon ) ko jo un se pehlay ki hain aur kash ( un ) zaalmon ko tum is waqt dekho jab yeh apne perwar-digaar ke samnay kharray hon ge aur aik dosray se radukad kar rahay hon ge. jo log kamzor samjhay jatay they woh barray logon se kahin ge ke agar tum nah hotay to hum zaroor momin ho jatay
  34,32,barray log kmzoron se kahin ge ke bhala hum ne tum ko hadaayat se jab woh tumahray paas aa chuki thi roka tha? ( nahi ) balkay tum hi gunehgaar they
  34,33,aur kamzor log barray logon se kahin ge ( nahi ) balkay ( tumhari ) raat din ki chalon ne ( hamein rok rakha tha ) jab tum hum se kehte they ke hum khuda se kufar karen aur is ka shareek banayen. aur jab woh azaab ko dekhen ge to dil mein pasheman hon ge. aur hum kafiroon ki gardnon mein taoq daal den ge. bas jo amal woh karte they un hi ka un ko badla miley ga
  34,34,aur hum ne kisi bastii mein koi darane wala nahi bheja magar wahan ke khush haal logon ne kaha ke jo cheez tum day kar beje gay ho hum is ke qaail nahi
  34,35,aur ( yeh bhi ) kehnay lagey ke hum bohat sa maal aur aulaad rakhtay hain aur hum ko azaab nahi hoga
  34,36,keh do ke mera rab jis ke liye chahta hai rozi farakh kardaita hai ( aur jis ke liye chahta hai ) tang kardaita hai lekin aksar log nahi jantay
  34,37,aur tumhara maal aur aulaad aisi cheez nahi ke tum ko hamara Maqarrab bana den. haan ( hamara Maqarrab woh hai ) jo imaan laya aur amal naik karta raha. aisay hi logon ko un ke aamaal ke sabab dugna badla miley ga aur woh khatir jama se balakhano+A3888 mein baithy hon ge
  34,38,jo log hamari aayton mein koshish karte hain ke hamein hara den woh azaab mein haazir kiye jayen ge
  34,39,keh do ke mera perwar-digaar apne bundon mein se jis ke liye chahta hai rozi farakh kardaita hai aur ( jis ke liye chahta hai ) tang kardaita hai aur tum jo cheez kharch karo ge woh is ka ( tumhe ) aiwz day ga. aur woh sab se behtar rizaq dainay wala hai
  34,40,aur jis din woh un sab ko jama kere ga phir firshton se farmaiye gakiya yeh log tum ko pooja karte they
  34,41,woh kahin ge to pak hai to hi hamara dost hai. nah yeh. balkay yeh jaanat ko pooja karte they. aur aksar unhi ko mantay they
  34,42,to aaj tum mein se koi kisi ko naffa aur nuqsaan pohanchanay ka ikhtiyar nahi rakhta. aur hum zaalmon se kahin ge ke dozakh ke azaab ka jis ko tum jhoot samajte they maza chako
  34,43,aur jab un ko hamari roshan ayatain parh kar sunai jati hain to kehte hain yeh aik ( aisa ) shakhs hai jo chahta hai ke jin cheezon ki tumahray baap dada parastishkiya karte they un se tum ko rok day aur ( yeh bhi ) kehte hain ke yeh ( quran ) mehez jhoot hai ( jo apni taraf se ) bana liya gaya hai. aur kafiroon ke paas jab haq aaya to is ke baray mein kehnay lagey ke yeh to Sarih jaadoo hai
  34,44,aur hum ne nah to un ( mushrikon ) ko kitaaben den jin ko yeh parhte hain aur nah tum se pehlay un ki taraf koi darane wala bheja magar unhon ne takzieeb ki
  34,45,aur jo log un se pehlay they unhon ne takzieeb ki thi aur jo kuch hum ne un ko diya tha yeh is ke dasvin hissay ko bhi nahi puhanche to unhon ne mere payghambaroon ko jhtlaya. so mera azaab kaisa howa
  34,46,keh do ke mein tumhe sirf aik baat ki nasiyaat karta hon ke tum khuda ke liye do do aur akailey akailey kharray hojao phir ghhor karo. tumahray Rafeeq ko soda nahi woh tum ko azaab sakht ( ke anay ) se pehlay sirf darane walay hain
  34,47,keh do ke mein ne tum se kuch sila manga ho to woh tum hi ko ( mubarak rahay ). mera sila khuda hi ke zimmay hai. aur woh har cheez se khabardaar hai
  34,48,keh do ke mera perwar-digaar oopar se haq utaarta hai ( aur woh ) ghaib ki baton ka jan-nay wala hai
  34,49,keh do ke haq aachuka aur ( mabood ) baatil nah to pehli baar peda karsaktha hai aur nah dobarah peda kere ga
  34,50,keh do ke agar mein gumraah hon to meri gumraahi ka zarrar mujhi ko hai. aur agar hadaayat par hon to yeh is ka tufail hai jo mera perwar-digaar meri taraf wahi bhejta hai. be shak woh suneney wala ( aur ) nazdeek hai
  34,51,aur kash tum dekho jab yeh ghabra jayen ge to ( azaab se ) bach nahi saken ge aur nazdeek hi se pakar liye jayen ge
  34,52,aur kahin ge ke hum is par imaan le aeye aur ( ab ) itni daur se un ka haath imaan ke lainay ko kyonkr poanch sakta hai
  34,53,aur pehlay to is se inkaar karte rahay aur ban dekhe daur hi se ( zan ke ) teer chillate rahay
  34,54,aur un mein aur un ki khwahish ki cheezon mein parda haail kardiya gaya jaissa ke pehlay un ke hum jnson sekiya gaya woh bhi uljan mein daalnay walay shak mein parre hue they
